description:
PLAY AS A VIRTUOSO CHEF IN THIS COOKING GAME, RENOVATE RESTAURANTS & CAFES!

Play Chef & Friends, a real cooking madness game! Transform chefs and renovate restaurants in the universe of the legendary Cooking Diary! Restore cafes and restaurants all over the world, become a head chef and leader of the restaurant restoration team!

In Chef & Friends you'll find:
- A fun puzzle game with great graphics and vibrant characters;
- Cooking madness in game levels: play and make delicious dishes from different world cuisines;
- Lots of unique cafes and restaurants in need of renovation and makeover;
- Renovation management: a cozy cafe with a homely atmosphere or a fancy restaurant – it's your choice;
- Restaurant owners makeover: help aspiring chefs find their own style and become cooking gurus;
- Tasty tales of friendship and love: adventures, puzzles, and intrigues;
- The fate of the cooking world is in your hands: protect restaurants and cafes from a greedy Fast Food Empire;
- A new game in the Cooking Diary universe: go beyond the culinary capital of Tasty Hills;
- Not just cooking and makeover: take part in fun events and play with other chefs;
- Glorious music unique to each restaurant and cafe;
- Free game updates: regular addition of new restaurants and game levels, fun events and valuable rewards;

Join us on social media
https://www.facebook.com/gaming/ChefAndFriendsMYTONA
https://www.instagram.com/chefandfriends_official/
https://twitter.com/chefandfriendsX
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrGnC_umzCITlCNxpcEANFA

The greedy billionaire Ethan Shark wants to get rid of all chefs and replace them with soulless robots. His Fast Food Empire is buying up and destroying restaurants and cafes all over the globe. If a restaurant owner refuses to sell their property, Ethan pits the Tasty Hills food critic against them. Chef, only you can save the world of real cooking!

Gather a team of professional restorers and protect restaurants and cafes from Ethan's greed. Help aspiring chefs pass the assessment of the Culinary Bulletin's restaurant critic: upgrade kitchens, renovate interiors, and give owners a makeover. Chef, hurry now to discover unforgettable culinary adventures! Play Chef & Friends!

Happy Diner Story is a delicious, newly designed time management game. Start by running a small restaurant, upgrade your chef, waiters and cooking equipment, open restaurants in every city in the world, and write the story of your culinary empire.
Different from common cooking games, this game simulates the process from cooking to serving, completely simulating the restaurant management gameplay, allowing you to immersively participate in every aspect of cooking. From the moment a customer enters the restaurant, the operation of the restaurant begins. Assigning tables to customers, customers ordering meals, serving snacks to customers, chefs personally cooking for customers, etc., a series of processes will be presented in the game. You can also upgrade waiters and chefs to make them more efficient and faster; upgrade dishes to make the food more delicious; upgrade restaurant equipment to accommodate more customers. Don't miss out on every detail, creating the perfect restaurant starts here.
Game features:
- Newly designed gameplay. Different from traditional cooking games, the immersive simulation will fascinate you;
- Everything can be upgraded. The elements you see: chefs, waiters, equipment, tables and chairs, etc., can all be upgraded to make your cooking process more comfortable;
- Customized decoration. Restore the restaurant's decoration design one-to-one, carefully arrange the restaurant decoration, all the decorations you see have been carefully created by us;
- Surprising props. Want a more enjoyable pass? It doesn't matter, you can use props to make the waiter run faster and satisfy customers' dish requirements at any time. There are also many surprise props waiting for you to discover;
- Rich activities and gameplay. We will regularly open limited-time events and launch limited items in conjunction with current festivals to greatly enrich the game content;
Run your restaurant, discover delicious food from all over the world, and realize your dream of being a chef here.

